flowchart LR
    Admin[Admin/API user] --> PolicyAPI[/POST /api/v1/policies/]
    PolicyAPI --> Loader[PolicyLoader]
    Loader --> DB[(policies + policy_versions)]
    Loader --> Cache[(Redis policy cache)]
    Loader --> Evaluator[OPAEvaluator hot-reload]
    Evaluator --> OPA[OPA policy data]
    Loader --> Event[Policy event publish]
    Event --> Sidecar[Sidecar policy watcher]
    PolicyAPI --> Response[Policy CRUD response]
    DB -->|error| Error[NRVQ-REG/NRVQ-API error path]
    Error --> Response
